        p The <a href="http://www.nba.com/suns/">Phoenix Suns</a> have been playing in the valley since 1968.

    //- Disneyland
    .flex-1of2
      .why.grey-light.text-drk
        .icon.disneyland
        p <a href="https://disneyland.disney.go.com/">Disneyland</a> is only a 6-hour drive from Phoenix. <a href="http://www.lasvegas.com/">Las Vegas</a>, 5 hours.

    //- Route 66
    .flex-1of2
      .why.brown.text-light
        .icon.route66
        p Arizona has the longest remaining section of <a href="http://www.historic66.com/">Route 66</a>, a total of 157 miles.

    //- Lakes
    .flex-1of2
      .why.tan.text-drk
        .icon.tube
        p Arizona has 128 lakes, including <a href="http://www.nps.gov/lake/index.htm">Lakes Mead</a>, <a href="http://azstateparks.com/Parks/LAHA/">Havasu</a>, and <a href="http://www.lakepowell.com/">Powell</a>.

    //- Beer
    .flex-1of2
      .why.navy-blue.text-light
        .icon.beer-mug
        p AZ has 60+ craft breweries, including the <a href="http://www.esquire.com/food-drink/drinks/a23543/arizona-wilderness-brewing-co-interview/">World’s Best New Brewery</a>.

    //- Thunderbird
    .flex-1of2
      .why.grey-light.text-drk
        .icon.tshirt.thunderbird
        p <a href="http://www.thunderbird.edu/">Thunderbird School of Global Management</a> ranked #1 International Full-time MBA in 2013.

    //- Memes
    .flex-1of2
      .why.tan.text-drk
        .icon.llamas
        p The memes you love come from Arizona, including <a href="http://www.abc15.com/news/region-west-valley/sun-city/llama-chase-in-arizona-video-watch-full-video-from-viral-sun-city-pursuit">Llama Drama</a> and <a href="http://www.grumpycats.com/">Grumpy Cat</a>.

    //- Dev Meetups
    .flex-1of2
      .why.umber.text-light
        .icon.terminal
        p Phoenix has awesome developer meetups like <a href="http://www.meetup.com/nodeaz/">NodeAZ</a>, <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Girl-Develop-It-Phoenix/">Girl Develop It</a>, <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Phoenix-JavaScript/">Phoenix JavaScript</a>, and <a href="http://phoenixios.wordpress.com/">PHX iOS Dev</a>.

    //- Food trucks
    .flex-1of2
      .why.red.text-light
        .icon.food-truck
        p Nearly <a href="http://phxstreetfood.org/">70 unique food trucks</a> serve Phoenix, including faves <a href="http://shortleashhotdogs.com/">Short Leash Hotdogs</a> and <a href="http://www.pizzapeopleaz.com/">Pizza People</a>.

    //- Pluto
