        p <a href="http://www.scottsdaleaz.gov/">Scottsdale</a> offers over 200 miles of <a href="http://www.scottsdaleaz.gov/preserve">Sonoran hiking trails</a>.

    //- Footers
    .flex-1of2
      footer.footer-desc.sky-blue.text-drk
        h2 Why Arizona?
        .text-left
          p Perks aside, the best thing about Arizona is the available room to grow. We’re a young state (the third youngest in our nation) and not until the 1950s did Phoenix truly begin to blossom.
          p We are establishing ourselves as a place not only for great weather, but for diverse culture, exceptional education, and competitive careers. There’s never been a better time for people to make an impact.
          p And really, a place is only as good as the people who live there. So come to Arizona for any of the awesome reasons we listed above, but stay for the community.
          p Join us and share what you love about Arizona with 
            <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23whyaz&amp;src=typd">#whyaz</a>.
        p.mt2
